          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-white/70 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <span class="font-medium text-indigo-900">Monday - Friday</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-indigo-700 bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">08:00 - 18:00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-white/70 p-4 rounded-lg">
