            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service Information -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-green-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            </svg>
            Service Information
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white/70 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">üí∞ Diagnosis</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-800">Only 30 BGN (15,32 ‚Ç¨) including on-site visit</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white/70 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">‚ö° Response Time</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-green-800">In most cases - same day</p>
            </div>
            
